 sparse correction.","Integration chain completed for `lowrank_residual_vq`: config whitelist + `_get_sae_class()` dispatch + class implementation.","Exact smoke test passed for `lowrank_residual_vq` at `K=24, EF=12` with forward/backward.","Quick behavioral diff check showed `lowrank_residual_vq` encode output is observably different from `lowrank_residual` on the same random input."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual_vq` is competitive but slightly worse at `K=24`, test `K=16` to see whether coarse residual coding helps more under tighter sparsity.","If `lowrank_residual_vq` wins at `K=24`, follow with `K=32` to see whether the gain persists across the mid-K band.","If it clearly loses at `K=24`, retire the low-rank-plus-discrete branch and move to a different mechanism family rather than tuning codebook size or router details."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
